parcel.name: KOREAN NFT
parcel.description:
11 artists have gathered here to create a unique art exhibit experience. Events will include drop parties, artist spotlights, solo exhibitions, group exhibitions, and many more. Artists who have founded this gallery are - 08am, So Youn Lee, NAKTA, Donglee Han, Yoyojin, I Draw Lily, Pika Park, Hyegyung Kim, Laylay, Autumn, and Yongoh Kim.


Architects: NAKTA, Donglee Han
Special thanks to: Hwaji, Loie, Sungsu
